2020年10月29日，[[法國|法國]][[尼斯|尼斯]][[尼斯聖母聖殿|聖母聖殿]]發生'''持刀襲擊事件'''，共造成三人死亡<ref>{{Cite web|title=法国再有2街头袭击案 刀手施袭3死多伤 枪手遭击毙  国际|url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/international/2020/10/29/372130|access-date=2021-12-18|date=2020-10-29|work=東方網 馬來西亞東方日報|language=zh-Hans|archive-date=2021-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211218074143/https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/international/2020/10/29/372130}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=法国尼斯发生持刀恐袭，致三人死亡|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20201029/nice-attack-france/|access-date=2021-12-18|date=2020-10-30|last=《纽约时报》|work=纽约时报中文网|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2021-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211224074219/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20201029/nice-attack-france/}}</ref>。當天早上，嫌犯坐火車抵达尼斯，並於8点29分进入[[尼斯聖母聖殿|尼斯聖母聖殿]]。他將一名60岁妇人斬首，另一名55歲男性也遭到割喉身亡。另有一名44岁定居法国的巴西女性逃出教堂，並来到附近一家酒吧，最終因伤势严重死亡。<ref>{{cite news |title=法国尼斯袭击案：一文了解袭击者、受害者与事件背景 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-54745400 |accessdate=2020-10-30 |archive-date=2020-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224192225/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-54745400 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Three dead as woman beheaded in knife attack at French church |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-france-security-nice/two-dead-in-knife-attack-in-french-church-official-say-terrorism-suspected-idUSKBN27E17D |work=Reuters |date=2020-10-29 |accessdate=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030020807/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-france-security-nice/two-dead-in-knife-attack-in-french-church-official-say-terrorism-suspected-idUSKBN27E17D |dead-url=no }}</ref>施襲者被警方開槍擊中后被捕，他亦是事件中唯一受傷的人士。<ref name=ind>{{cite news |title=Nice stabbings: Woman decapitated and others killed in France knife attack |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/nice-stabbings-attack-france-today-deaths-injured-latest-b1417706.html |work=Independent |date=2020-10-29 |accessdate=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029150916/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/nice-stabbings-attack-france-today-deaths-injured-latest-b1417706.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

尼斯市長將事件定調為恐怖襲擊，他稱施襲者被捕時不斷高喊“[[真主至大|真主至大]]”（{{lang|en|Allahu Akbar}}）。事發時正在開會的[[國民議會_(法國)|法國國民議會]]為受害者進行一分鐘默哀儀式。<ref>{{cite news |title=Nice attack: Mayor says deadly stabbing points to terrorism |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54729957 |work=BBC |date=2020-10-29 |accessdate=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029095700/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54729957 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=ind/>

==疑犯==
疑犯卜拉欣·阿维萨维（Brahim Aouissaoui）是21歲男子，來自[[突尼斯|突尼斯]]，於2020年9月14日乘偷渡船來到[[意大利|意大利]]，并10月28日抵达尼斯。突尼斯反恐官员表示，并未将嫌疑人列入突尼斯反恐名单上，因此法国情报部门也不知道阿维萨维<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54742403 |title=France attack: Attacker arrived from Tunisia days ago |publisher=BBC |date=2020-10-29 |accessdate=2020-10-30 |archive-date=2020-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224192247/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54742403 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

